  "body": "The geth team is currently trying to integrate the erigon client into [hive](https://github.com/ethereum/hive) (our testing rig) so that we can run behaviour / spec conformance tests on erigon along with the rest of the eth1 clients as part of our CI. The easiest way for us to integrate erigon would be if there were an official up-to-date docker image on [dockerhub](https://hub.docker.com/) to pull from as a base so that we can build on top of it to make it runnable as part of the hive suite.\r\n",
